<H1>Mary, Gary &amp; Lucy</H1>


<b>Mary the Contrary</b> is a player, who always want to tweak the game. Typical situations include:
• 
• flavour
• sourcebooks from older versions
• lore from older versions
• tertiary races
• tertiary classes
• alternate backgrounds

Adequate solutions ought to be based on
• clear sistinction between SRD
• creativity
• sensible interpretation of exisisting 5erules
• RAW, RAI & RAF
Variant races, Custom Origin & Custom Lineage (TCoE p.)
Variant clases
Optional Feat Rule (PHB)



